      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "IT'S A TEASE (2) has been out of the placings last two but prior to that clocked a fast 29.66 win over 515m at this track. Can measure up on top win three back. ZIPPING LYNDY (3) turned in a plain performance last time when eighth at Taree Super Track over 525m behind Kiarni Phoenix (31.19) in a NG. Placed at her previous run. Good beginner aided by a nice draw. Key runner on best form. FASCINATE SUZIE (1) had been going along well winning a Grade 5 three back then placing at Wentworth Park before missing the frame latest when sixth (30.52) at Wentworth Park. Safe beginner and drawn well on the inside. Can turn it around this time. CURYO DANCER (7) cannot be underestimated.",
